FPL segment, Corporate and Other , NEER and Gulf Power .
FPL's net income increased by $316 million in 2021 primarily reflecting higher results at the FPL segment and at Gulf Power . The FPL segment's
increase in net income for 2021 was primarily driven by continued investments in plant in service  and other property . Gulf Power's increase in net
