Redeemable Noncontrolling Interests  – Certain subsidiaries of NextEra Energy Resources sold Class B membership interests in entities that
have ownership interests in wind generation as well as solar and solar plus battery storage facilities to third-party investors. As specified in the
respective limited liability company agreements, if, subject to certain contingencies, certain events occur , including, among others, those that
