In September 2020, NEE sold $2.0 billion of equity units (initially consisting of Corporate Units). Each equity unit has a stated amount of $50 and
consists of a contract to purchase NEE common stock (stock purchase contract) and, initially , a 5% undivided  beneficial ownership interest in a
